data.name: Cold Borscht (Holodnik)
data.quickTastyDescription: A refreshing cold beet soup, vibrant in color and flavor, perfect for warm days.
detailedCookingInstructions: In a large bowl, combine the cooked and diced beets, diced cucumber, sliced radishes, chopped green onions, and dill.
In another bowl, mix the vegetable broth, Greek yogurt (or sour cream), lemon juice, salt, and pepper until well blended.
Pour the broth mixture into the vegetable mixture and stir to combine.
Chill in the refrigerator for at least 1 hour before serving for the best flavor.
Serve cold, garnished with additional dill if desired.
